CMAKE_MAKE_PROGRAM  make nmake msdev devenv  *** HAS TO BE IN CACHE for try compile to work
CMAKE_BUILD_TYPE   Debug Release RelWithDebInfo MinSizeRel
BUILD_COMMAND needs to be removed

